# Config Rules

- Treat `config/` as the main customization layer for this repo.
- Put model/provider settings, gateway defaults, agent lists, and skills loading in `config/openclaw.json`.
- Put agent behavior and bootstrap instructions in `config/workspaces/**`.
- Preserve the default agent topology (`main`, `coder`, `researcher`, `planner`) unless the change intentionally migrates it everywhere.
- Prefer wrapper-level config changes over modifying the OpenClaw source fork for Messy Virgo-specific behavior.
